WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.419
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.420 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.695
=Episode 20=

00:01:11.259 --> 00:01:12.780
Hear my command.

00:01:13.339 --> 00:01:15.978
Search every inch of the ground.

00:01:15.979 --> 00:01:17.459
If we fail,

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:20.739
none of us will live to see tomorrow.

00:01:21.100 --> 00:01:22.260
Yes.

00:01:23.020 --> 00:01:24.860
Looking for the jade ruyi?

00:01:33.100 --> 00:01:34.500
Song Zhiyun.

00:01:34.979 --> 00:01:36.224
You truly have no fear of death.

00:01:36.225 --> 00:01:38.674
Gu Chengye has already
destroyed himself,

00:01:38.675 --> 00:01:41.019
yet you still refuse
to let the Shengtang Guild go.

00:01:42.740 --> 00:01:44.060
Grand Commandant Gao,

00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:46.459
if you have the courage,

00:01:46.499 --> 00:01:47.780
kill me.

00:01:48.180 --> 00:01:49.539
But if I die,

00:01:49.540 --> 00:01:51.379
that jade ruyi

00:01:51.380 --> 00:01:52.179
will appear

00:01:52.180 --> 00:01:54.860
on the desk of the Court
of Judicial Review at dawn.

00:01:55.262 --> 00:01:56.423
By then,

00:01:56.660 --> 00:01:59.700
your superiors' secrets and crimes

00:01:59.740 --> 00:02:01.780
will be laid bare.

00:02:02.139 --> 00:02:04.060
What do you want?

00:02:06.125 --> 00:02:07.220
Gao Deng,

00:02:07.287 --> 00:02:09.699
you are not in a position to bargain.

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:13.699
Take me to the true power
behind the Shengtang Guild.

00:02:21.580 --> 00:02:24.500
You managed to find my jade ruyi.

00:02:25.659 --> 00:02:28.300
Impressive indeed.

00:02:28.580 --> 00:02:30.500
Your Highness flatters me.

00:02:30.939 --> 00:02:32.900
However clever I may be,

00:02:33.140 --> 00:02:34.659
I never imagined

00:02:35.059 --> 00:02:37.259
that the revered
Imperial Dowager Consort

00:02:37.539 --> 00:02:38.259
would be

00:02:38.260 --> 00:02:41.020
the one pulling the strings
behind the Shengtang Guild.

00:02:44.539 --> 00:02:46.659
A serpent's heart behind a pious face.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.721
No matter how many sutras one recites,

00:02:48.740 --> 00:02:50.859
true blessing will never follow.

00:02:51.539 --> 00:02:52.699
Your Highness,

00:02:53.059 --> 00:02:55.020
you should understand that.

00:02:56.860 --> 00:02:59.099
Remarkable nerve.

00:03:05.700 --> 00:03:06.818
You and she

00:03:06.819 --> 00:03:09.020
are indeed alike.

00:03:11.140 --> 00:03:12.419
Back then,

00:03:12.420 --> 00:03:15.379
when I first met her,

00:03:15.700 --> 00:03:17.179
I thought she was

00:03:17.180 --> 00:03:19.939
clever and obedient,

00:03:19.980 --> 00:03:21.938
so resilient,

00:03:21.939 --> 00:03:23.379
so beautiful.

00:03:24.700 --> 00:03:26.780
Just like you.

00:03:27.339 --> 00:03:29.300
The kind that makes others

00:03:30.539 --> 00:03:32.579
admire

00:03:32.580 --> 00:03:33.819
and envy.

00:03:33.980 --> 00:03:35.500
Twelve years ago,

00:03:35.860 --> 00:03:37.180
it was you

00:03:37.700 --> 00:03:40.139
who killed the Duchess,

00:03:40.260 --> 00:03:41.300
was it not?

00:03:44.659 --> 00:03:47.338
You would do well
to think before you speak.

00:03:47.339 --> 00:03:49.058
Such words

00:03:49.059 --> 00:03:51.379
can cost you your head.

00:03:53.779 --> 00:03:56.379
I know exactly what I am saying.

00:03:57.460 --> 00:03:58.699
Before this,

00:03:58.900 --> 00:04:00.378
what Zhou Zihua said before he died

00:04:00.379 --> 00:04:02.338
kept circling in my mind.

00:04:02.339 --> 00:04:03.900
It puzzled me.

00:04:04.659 --> 00:04:06.020
Until later,

00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:09.099
when I pieced everything together,

00:04:09.379 --> 00:04:11.060
it became clear.

00:04:12.137 --> 00:04:14.659
(Haitang Madam)
The silhouette hidden within the Beauty Portrait.

00:04:18.412 --> 00:04:19.661
Gu Chengye said

00:04:19.662 --> 00:04:21.619
there were bloodstains
on the white sash.

00:04:22.979 --> 00:04:25.099
And when I found the jade ruyi,

00:04:25.140 --> 00:04:27.900
I noticed a nearly imperceptible chip.

00:04:28.580 --> 00:04:30.460
That confirmed my suspicion.

00:04:30.975 --> 00:04:33.419
What has that to do with me?

00:04:38.339 --> 00:04:40.579
If Your Highness finds
your memory unclear,

00:04:40.580 --> 00:04:43.032
then think of it as a story.

00:04:43.700 --> 00:04:44.859
This story

00:04:46.339 --> 00:04:49.020
begins twelve years ago.

00:04:50.339 --> 00:04:52.700
Twelve years ago,
the Duchess founded the Shengtang Guild

00:04:53.339 --> 00:04:54.738
to gather women from across the realm

00:04:54.739 --> 00:04:56.299
to learn and refine their talents.

00:04:56.900 --> 00:04:57.700
And you,

00:04:57.979 --> 00:04:59.340
Dowager Consort Wu,

00:04:59.739 --> 00:05:01.820
a favored guest in her household,

00:05:02.060 --> 00:05:03.859
harbored darker intent.

00:05:04.859 --> 00:05:07.220
When you learned
the Duchess was gravely ill,

00:05:07.500 --> 00:05:09.380
and that the red rashes would not fade,

00:05:09.450 --> 00:05:11.499
you spread rumors everywhere,

00:05:11.900 --> 00:05:13.619
claiming she had a disgraceful disease.

00:05:15.979 --> 00:05:17.739
I trusted you so deeply,

00:05:17.979 --> 00:05:19.579
and you used my Shengtang Guild

00:05:19.580 --> 00:05:21.099
for such schemes.

00:05:21.339 --> 00:05:23.619
I will make this known to the world,

00:05:23.750 --> 00:05:26.419
so all may see your true face.

00:05:50.612 --> 00:05:52.732
You are naive.

00:05:56.099 --> 00:05:57.419
Under this imperial city,

00:05:57.580 --> 00:05:59.260
is there truly no law?

00:06:01.712 --> 00:06:04.771
Clean it all up. Otherwise...

00:06:07.539 --> 00:06:08.780
Yes.

00:06:27.659 --> 00:06:28.820
In the end,

00:06:29.179 --> 00:06:31.499
you forced Zhou Zihua
to stage the scene,

00:06:32.062 --> 00:06:33.879
to make it appear

00:06:33.940 --> 00:06:34.858
that the Duchess

00:06:34.859 --> 00:06:36.299
unable to bear the slander

00:06:36.739 --> 00:06:37.539
and took her own life.

00:06:37.659 --> 00:06:39.299
But you overlooked one thing.

00:06:39.979 --> 00:06:41.499
Zhou Zihua.

00:06:44.299 --> 00:06:46.107
Zhou Zihua.

00:06:50.339 --> 00:06:51.536
A stubborn stone,

00:06:51.537 --> 00:06:54.419
impossible to shape.

00:06:55.979 --> 00:06:57.858
Just like his

00:06:57.859 --> 00:06:59.532
wretched master.

00:07:00.179 --> 00:07:02.460
They all deserved it.

00:07:03.250 --> 00:07:04.731
Your Highness,

00:07:05.175 --> 00:07:06.899
you killed the Duchess

00:07:06.900 --> 00:07:08.245
and countless women,

00:07:08.380 --> 00:07:11.070
then used the Beauty Portrait
and the register to coerce officials.

00:07:11.979 --> 00:07:12.978
All for

00:07:12.979 --> 00:07:14.911
your unworthy son, Prince Gong,

00:07:14.912 --> 00:07:18.520
(Imperial Gift to Prince Gong:
Only diligence earns the mandate)

00:07:21.900 --> 00:07:23.020
Enough.

00:07:33.060 --> 00:07:35.780
Where is the jade ruyi?

00:07:36.260 --> 00:07:38.260
If you do not hand it over,

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:41.700
I can end your life here and now.

00:07:42.339 --> 00:07:43.699
The ruyi is hidden

00:07:43.700 --> 00:07:45.220
where none would easily find it.

00:07:45.739 --> 00:07:46.658
Release Gu Chengye,

00:07:46.659 --> 00:07:47.979
and I will surrender it.

00:07:48.260 --> 00:07:49.299
Otherwise,

00:07:50.940 --> 00:07:52.299
that ruyi

00:07:52.820 --> 00:07:55.179
will reach His Majesty's desk directly.

00:08:17.620 --> 00:08:19.260
Tell me,

00:08:19.380 --> 00:08:21.700
when someone walks in here shortly,

00:08:22.299 --> 00:08:24.780
will it be men sent
by the Emperor to arrest me,

00:08:25.739 --> 00:08:28.659
or Gu Chengye coming to his death?

00:09:09.699 --> 00:09:10.820
Gu Chengye.

00:09:14.939 --> 00:09:17.859
Worthy of the Commander
of the Imperial Guard,

00:09:17.860 --> 00:09:20.019
loyal and steadfast.

00:09:20.020 --> 00:09:22.458
Gu Chengye, hand over the jade ruyi,

00:09:22.459 --> 00:09:23.739
and I will release her.

00:09:26.340 --> 00:09:29.060
Release her, and it is yours.

00:09:31.140 --> 00:09:33.300
You are in no position to bargain.

00:09:33.500 --> 00:09:35.420
I can take it myself.

00:09:37.380 --> 00:09:40.058
Gu Chengye has entered the palace armed,

00:09:40.059 --> 00:09:41.361
with intent to rebel.

00:09:41.362 --> 00:09:43.032
Seize him.